messages.messageBody:
woke up early this am and got a declined membership to a group
and went out of room and my computer crashed I mean crash! said
complete hard drive failer. wont boot evenn with a disk nota I run 3
virus protecters. (one I pay thru the nose for) 2 fire walls and the
puter is exatly one year and 3 days old.
I also start a 20 streach at work tue of 5 am. to 4 p.m
I got hubbys puter up and running but I havent had it net ready in
over a year so dont trust it . I will try and change to diegest to
stop the bouncing that happens when mailbox gets to full.
I doubt the crash has much to do with. the decline letter I recived.
but they had been having problems is why they closed there
membership. It probley due to the timing of the warenty . lol it
did tell me to take off any thing I had recently put in computer ans
I hadn't any thing new.
this is just my week lol after I went upstair I also descovered my
fridge had gave up on me. Then went to work to find I need to fix a
ice cream machine . not my day to day.
maybe tommorow will be better.
Dee
